trans-unit.source: Allows a custom override of the <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.DependencyObject.SetValue*> logic associated with a dependency property that is defined on a dependency object.
trans-unit.target: 사용자 지정 재정의 허용 하면는 <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.DependencyObject.SetValue*>종속성 개체에 정의 된 종속성 속성과 연결 된 논리.</xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.DependencyObject.SetValue*>

trans-unit.source: > [!NOTE] > [!INCLUDE[DeprecatedContent](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)] The implementation of this delegate can be set to the <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.PropertyMetadata.SetValueOverride%2A> property of <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.PropertyMetadata> while calling <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.DependencyProperty.Register%2A> or <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.DependencyProperty.RegisterAttached%2A>.
trans-unit.target: > [!NOTE] > [!INCLUDE[DeprecatedContent](~/add/includes/ajax-current-ext-md.md)]이 대리자의 구현은 <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.PropertyMetadata.SetValueOverride%2A> <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.PropertyMetadata> <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.DependencyProperty.Register%2A>나 <xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.DependencyProperty.RegisterAttached%2A>.</xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.DependencyProperty.RegisterAttached%2A> </xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.DependencyProperty.Register%2A> 를 호출 하는 동안</xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.PropertyMetadata> 의 속성</xref:System.Workflow.ComponentModel.PropertyMetadata.SetValueOverride%2A> 으로 설정할 수 있습니다.
